{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-binfeng-007__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-binfeng-007", "source_id": "guofeng-binfeng-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "poem", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·豳風·007.1", "text_original": "狼跋其胡，載疐其尾。公孫碩膚，赤舄几几。\n狼疐其尾，載跋其胡。公孫碩膚，德音不瑕。", "text_normalized": "狼跋其胡，載疐其尾。公孫碩膚，赤舄几几。\n狼疐其尾，載跋其胡。公孫碩膚，德音不瑕。", "notes": "狼跋 Chinese poem 1."}
